Following steps are necessary for development:

JBOSS AS 7:
http://download.jboss.org/jbossas/7.1/jboss-as-7.1.0.CR1b/jboss-as-7.1.0.CR1b.zip

Getting Started Instructions:
https://docs.jboss.org/author/display/AS7/Getting+Started+Developing+Applications+Guide

JBOSS Tools:
http://sourceforge.net/projects/jboss/files/JBossTools/JBossTools3.3.0.x/jbosstools-3.3.0.M5.aggregate-Update-2011-12-14_19-42-13-H61.zip

Installation instructions for the ZIP file (simply install everything offered in the repository):
http://www.jboss.org/tools/download/dev


Demo Applications for JBOSS AS 7:
http://download.jboss.org/jbossas/7.1/jboss-as-7.1.0.Beta1b/jboss-as-quickstarts-7.1.0.Beta1b-dist.zip
